    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock for precise torque distribution. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and shim-and-bucket valve clearance adjustment to ensure optimal volumetric efficiency. The chassis remains composed with upgraded bushings and reinforced rear subframe mounting points to mitigate common floor-pan fatigue. While displaying minor aesthetic patina, the mechanical synchronization and throttle mapping are exceptionally sharp, offering a pure analog driving experience.",
