      "description": "This meticulously maintained 2018 BMW X5 xDrive35i presents a stunning balance of luxury and utility. The Mineral White Metallic exterior retains a deep, reflective shine, showing only minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with responsible highway driving. Inside, the Mocha Dakota leather seats remain firm and supple, free of cracks or significant wear, while the Fineline Oak wood trim adds a warm, premium touch to the cabin. Every electronic feature, including the iDrive navigation system and the panoramic moonroof, operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the 3.0L TwinPower Turbo engine runs smoothly, backed by a complete service history from certified technicians. The vehicle sits on a set of premium all-season tires with ample tread remaining, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a smoke-free, garage-kept SUV that offers the prestige of a high-end European vehicle with the peace of mind that comes from proactive maintenance.",
